3|title=Top Singoli \u2013 Classifica settimanale WK 13|publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]]|language=Italian|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| 85\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Lithuania ([[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.agata.lt/lt/naujienos/savaites-klausomiausi-2020w11/|title=2020 11-os SAVAIT\u0116S (kovo 6-12 d.) SINGL\u0172 TOP100.|publisher=[[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]]|language=Lithuanian|accessdate=March 18, 2020}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysia ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/RecordingIndustryMalaysia/photos/pcb.3299042760123071/3299042616789752/?type=3&theater|title=Top 20 Most Streamed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=March 15, 2020}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Mexico Airplay]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/mexico/2020-03-14 | work = [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]| title = Mexico Airplay|accessdate=March 12, 2020}}</ref>\n| 11\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch40|15|year=2020|week=13|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|16|artist=Doja Cat|song=Say So|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4832|title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=March 16, 2020|accessdate=March 14, 2020}}</ref>\n| 3\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Norway ([[VG-lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://topplista.no/charts/singles/2020-w13/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 13, 2020|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| 25\n|-\n{{single chart|Poland|32|chartid=3346|year=2020|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Portugal|17|artist=Doja Cat|rowheader=true|song=Say So|accessdate=March 29, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Romania ([[Airplay 100 (Romania)|Airplay 100]])<!--Please do not change this to Romanian Top 100 or Media Forest. The Airplay 100 is Romania's national singles chart from 2012 onwards. For further information, see WP:GOODCHARTS--><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kissfm.ro/podcasturi/6812|title=Airplay 100 \u2013 1 martie 2020|publisher=[[Kiss FM (Romania)|Kiss FM]]|language=Romanian|accessdate=March 2, 2020|date=March 1, 2020}}</ref>\n| 32\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|11|date=20200320|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Singapore ([[Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|RIAS]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|title=RIAS International Top Charts Week 11|publisher=Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323065637/https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|archive-date=March 23, 2020}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n{{single chart|Slovakdigital|26|year=2020|week=10|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 10, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Spain ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|PROMUSICAE]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elportaldemusica.es/lists/top-100-canciones/2020/12|title=Top 100 Canciones: Semana 12|publisher=[[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a]]|accessdate=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n| 94\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Sweden ([[Sverigetopplistan]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2020&dspp=13|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 13|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n| 31\n|-\n{{single chart|Switzerland|24|artist=Doja Cat|rowheader=true|song=Say So|accessdate=March 30, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|UK|7|date=20200327|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref>https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9346375/weeknd-blinding-lights-number-one-hot-100</ref><ref name=\"Hot 100\">{{ci